{"type": "article", "id": 13382, "title": "小巧减湿器", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-12T07:13:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122447bOsAnYTpEhQm2xqa.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tGoogle 一下“减湿器”，你估计能找到一大片结果，但详细大部分与你的室内装修格格不入。250 Design 最近推出了一款基本没什么“存在感”的减湿器，小巧的外形和鲜艳的颜色让它们看起来轻松活泼，可以随意放在家里任何一个角落，后面的设计可以让它挂在墙上不容易丢失，还可以放在需要减湿的抽屉里面。这是<a href=\"http://250.or.kr/portfolio/natural-dehumidifier/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141157bf74TjUlgRIrLuN0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141158fRNIHq2VrUOEuviP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261411596udIH8bYKtVm29pN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141159BKECxjefb6LtXGmN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141200KLm8W1dJB3xbHlOA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141200LKkMCqmDIjbi3rlu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141201urA754WiHcbXIUpP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141201G2c8lRTmfn9VW4rJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}